outliers <- function(x) {
  qnt <- quantile(x, probs=c(.25, .75), na.rm = TRUE)
  H <- 2 * IQR(x, na.rm = TRUE)
  x[x < (qnt[1] - H)] <- qnt[1] - H
  x[x > (qnt[2] + H)] <- qnt[2] + H
  return(x)
}

# 创建结果向量====
result_vector <- vector()

# 定义函数，传入数据集和变量名
median_iqr <- function(data, var_name) {
  # 根据 td_pigd 列的值进行分组
  td_data <- data[data$td_pigd == "td", ]
  no_td_data <- data[data$td_pigd == "no_td", ]
  
  # 计算中位数
  td_med <- median(td_data[[var_name]])
  no_td_med <- median(no_td_data[[var_name]])
  
  # 计算四分位距
  td_q1 <- quantile(td_data[[var_name]], 0.25)
  td_q3 <- quantile(td_data[[var_name]], 0.75)
  td_iqr <- td_q3 - td_q1
  no_td_q1 <- quantile(no_td_data[[var_name]], 0.25)
  no_td_q3 <- quantile(no_td_data[[var_name]], 0.75)
  no_td_iqr <- no_td_q3 - no_td_q1
  
  # 使用 Mann-Whitney U 检验比较两组之间的差异
  p_val <- wilcox.test(td_data[[var_name]], no_td_data[[var_name]])$p.value
  
  # 输出结果
  result <- list(paste0(round(td_med, 4), " (", round(td_q1, 4), "-", round(td_q3, 4), ")"), 
                 paste0(round(no_td_med, 4), " (", round(no_td_q1, 4), "-", round(no_td_q3, 4), ")"), 
                 round(p_val, 4))
  
  unlist(c(var_name, result))
}

  # 将结果添加到向量中
  result_vector <- c(result_vector, median_iqr(statistic_BL, var))

#Synthetic Minority Over-Sampling Technique====
smote_BL <- subset(data_clear, EVENT_ID=="BL")
desp_ref <- smote_BL[,c("td_pigd","tremor","MCI_testscores","NP1APAT","NP1FATG","EDUCYRS","ageonset","ess","MSEADLG","DOMSIDERight","stai","asyn","SDMTOTAL","rigidity","gen","lns","scopa","fampd_new","quip","sft","bjlot")]
desp_ref$NP1FATG <- as.numeric(desp_ref$NP1FATG)-1
desp_ref$NP1APAT <- as.numeric(desp_ref$NP1APAT)-1
rec1 <- recipe(td_pigd~.,data = desp_ref)
table(desp_ref$td_pigd)
## 
## no_td    td 
##   103   256
set.seed(2023)
smote <- rec1 %>% 
  step_smote(td_pigd, over_ratio = 1) %>%
  prep() %>%
  bake(new_data = NULL)

smote <- smote %>%
  mutate_at(vars(matches("stai|tremor|rigidity|EDUCYRS|MSEADLG|ess|NP1FATG|scopa|rem|NP1APAT|sft|MCI_testscores|lns|SDMTOTAL|fampd_new|moca|bjlot|DOMSIDERight|gen|quip")), ~round(.)) %>%
  mutate_at(vars(matches("stai|tremor|rigidity|EDUCYRS|MSEADLG|ess|NP1FATG|scopa|rem|NP1APAT|sft|MCI_testscores|lns|SDMTOTAL|fampd_new|moca|bjlot|DOMSIDERight|gen|quip")), ~as.integer(.))

smote[,c("tremor","rigidity","EDUCYRS","stai","ess","asyn","MSEADLG","scopa","sft","lns","SDMTOTAL","ageonset","bjlot","quip")] <- scale(smote[,c("tremor","rigidity","EDUCYRS","stai","ess","asyn","MSEADLG","scopa","sft","lns","SDMTOTAL","ageonset","bjlot","quip")])

table(smote$td_pigd)
## 
## no_td    td 
##   256   256
#Divide the baseline data into training and test sets----
set.seed(2023)
train_sub = sample(nrow(smote),3/4*nrow(smote))
train_data = smote[train_sub,]
test_data = smote[-train_sub,]
train_data <- as.data.frame(train_data)
test_data <- as.data.frame(test_data)
BL_trainTask <- makeClassifTask(data = train_data, target = "td_pigd")
BL_testTask <- makeClassifTask(data = test_data, target = "td_pigd")

# mlr包的逻辑回归
set.seed(2023)
logReg <- makeLearner("classif.logreg",predict.type="prob")#指定learner
logRegModel <- train(logReg, BL_trainTask)#训练模型
# 预测测试集数据
set.seed(2023)
logReg_pred <- predict(logRegModel, BL_testTask)

#总的输出结果
logReg_test_label <- ifelse(logReg_pred$data$truth == "td", 1, 0)
logReg_test_pred <- ifelse(logReg_pred$data$response == "td", 1, 0)
#logReg_roc <- roc(logReg_test_label, logReg_test_pred)
logReg_roc <- roc(logReg_test_label, logReg_pred$data$prob.no_td)
## Setting levels: control = 0, case = 1
## Setting direction: controls > cases
logReg_result <- confusionMatrix(logReg_pred$data$response, logReg_pred$data$truth,positive = "no_td")

#减少asyn----
desp_ref <- smote_BL[,c("td_pigd","tremor","MCI_testscores","NP1APAT","NP1FATG","EDUCYRS","ageonset",
                              "ess","MSEADLG","DOMSIDERight","stai","SDMTOTAL",
                              "rigidity","gen","lns","scopa","fampd_new","quip","sft","bjlot")]


desp_ref$NP1FATG <- as.numeric(desp_ref$NP1FATG)-1
desp_ref$NP1APAT <- as.numeric(desp_ref$NP1APAT)-1
rec1 <- recipe(td_pigd~.,data = desp_ref)
set.seed(2023)
smote <- rec1 %>% 
  step_smote(td_pigd, over_ratio = 1) %>%
  prep() %>%
  bake(new_data = NULL)

smote <- smote %>%
  mutate_at(vars(matches("tremor|stai|EDUCYRS|MSEADLG|ess|rigidity|NP1FATG|scopa|rem|NP1APAT|sft|MCI_testscores|lns|SDMTOTAL|fampd_new|moca|bjlot|DOMSIDERight|gen|quip")), ~round(.)) %>%
  mutate_at(vars(matches("tremor|stai|EDUCYRS|MSEADLG|ess|rigidity|NP1FATG|scopa|rem|NP1APAT|sft|MCI_testscores|lns|SDMTOTAL|fampd_new|moca|bjlot|DOMSIDERight|gen|quip")), ~as.integer(.))
smote[,c("tremor","EDUCYRS","ageonset","ess","MSEADLG","stai","SDMTOTAL","rigidity","lns","scopa","quip","sft","bjlot")] <- scale(smote[,c("tremor","EDUCYRS","ageonset","ess","MSEADLG","stai","SDMTOTAL","rigidity","lns","scopa","quip","sft","bjlot")])



#划分训练集和测试集----
set.seed(2023)
train_sub = sample(nrow(smote),3/4*nrow(smote))
train_data = smote[train_sub,]
test_data = smote[-train_sub,]
train_data <- as.data.frame(train_data)
test_data <- as.data.frame(test_data)
BL_trainTask <- makeClassifTask(data = train_data, target = "td_pigd")
BL_testTask <- makeClassifTask(data = test_data, target = "td_pigd")

  kFold <- makeResampleDesc(method = "CV", iters = 5, stratify = TRUE)
  
  # 进行交叉验证
  kFoldCV <- resample(learner = psvm, task = exper_task,
                      resampling = kFold, measures = list(auc,f1))
